---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Off-Peak Hours Incentive RM15/Trip: How Prime Mover Financing Maximizes Profit',
  slug: 'off-peak-rm15-prime-mover-profit',
  excerpt: 'Malaysia offers RM15/trip off-peak incentive for prime movers entering major highways during non-peak hours. Learn how to structure financing to maximize this government incentive and boost your haulage profitability.',
  date: '2025-01-23',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 7,
  category: 'Prime Mover Financing',
  image: '/images/blog/prime-mover-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['off-peak hours', 'prime mover profit', 'government incentive', '0% down payment', 'haulage optimization'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Prime Mover Financing</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>The RM15/Trip Incentive: Government Pays You to Drive Off-Peak</h2>

      <p>Malaysia's highways are congested during peak hours. 6am-10am and 4pm-8pm: traffic jams, delays, frustration.</p>

      <p>The government's solution: incentivize heavy vehicles to drive during off-peak hours.</p>

      <p><strong>The Offer:</strong> RM15 per trip for prime movers entering major highways during off-peak hours (10pm-6am).</p>

      <p>For a prime operator making 300 trips monthly, that's RM4,500 in additional profit—purely for adjusting your schedule.</p>

      <h2>How the Off-Peak Incentive Works</h2>

      <h3>Program Details</h3>

      <p><strong>Eligible Vehicles:</strong>
      <br>• Prime movers (head trucks)
      <br>• Heavy lorries (5-ton and above)
      <br>• Trailers and container carriers</p>

      <p><strong>Eligible Highways:</strong>
      <br>• North-South Expressway (PLUS)
      <br>• AKLEH Highway
      <br>• KESAS Highway
      <br>• Other major highways (check latest list with JPJ)</p>

      <p><strong>Off-Peak Hours:</strong>
      <br>• Night: 10:00pm - 6:00am
      <br>• Incentive rate: RM15 per highway entry</p>

      <h3>Application Process</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Register with JPJ/LLM (Lembaga Lebuhraya Malaysia)
        <li>Install on-board unit (OBM) tracking device
        <li>Obtain off-peak vehicle sticker
        <li>Submit monthly trip logs
        <li>Receive incentive payment monthly</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The Profitability Math: Off-Peak Operations</h2>

      <h3>Revenue Impact Calculation</h3>

      <p><strong>Current Operations (Peak Hours Only):</strong>
      <br>• Trips per day: 2
      <br>• Revenue per trip: RM1,500
      <br>• Daily revenue: RM3,000
      <br>• Monthly revenue (25 days): RM75,000
      <br><strong>Off-Peak Incentive:</strong> RM0 (not participating)</p>

           <p><strong>Off-Peak Operations (Same 2 Trips, Adjusted Schedule):</strong>
      <br>• Trips per day: 2 (now 10pm-6am)
      <br>• Revenue per trip: RM1,500 (same rate)
      <br>• Daily revenue: RM3,000
      <br>• Monthly revenue (25 days): RM75,000
      <br><strong>Off-Peak Incentive:</strong> RM750/day (RM15 × 2 trips × 25 days)
      <br><strong>Monthly Bonus:</strong> RM18,750</p>

      <p><strong>Annual Bonus:</strong> RM225,000 additional profit</p>

      <h3>Additional Benefits Beyond RM15/Trip</h3>

      <p><strong>Fuel Savings:</strong>
      <br>• No traffic congestion = consistent speed
      <br>• Peak hours: stop-and-go driving increases fuel consumption 15-20%
      <br>• Off-peak: steady speed = optimal fuel efficiency
      <br><strong>Fuel Savings:</strong> RM500-RM1,000 monthly</p>

      <p><strong>Time Savings:</strong>
      <br>• Peak hours: 2 hours per trip (traffic delays)
      <br>• Off-peak: 1.5 hours per trip (clear roads)
      <br>• Time saved: 30 minutes per trip
      <br><strong>Result:</strong> Can fit 3 trips in same time (if demand exists) = RM1,500 additional revenue per day</p>

      <p><strong>Driver Benefits:</strong>
      <br>• Less stressful driving (no congestion frustration)
      <br>• Better sleep schedule (night operations)
      <br>• Higher driver retention</p>

      <h2>Financing Off-Peak Operations: What You Need</h2>

      <h3>OBU (On-Board Unit) Installation</h3>

      <p><strong>Required Equipment:</strong>
      <br>• GPS tracking device
      <br>• Highway entry detection sensor
      <br>• Data transmission unit
      <br><strong>Cost:</strong> RM2,000-RM3,500 per prime mover</p>

      <p><strong>Financing Solution:</strong>
      <br>• Include OBU in prime mover financing
      <br>• RM3,500 spread over 5-year term = RM70/month additional
      <br>• Off-peak incentive (RM750/month) more than covers OBU cost</p>

      <h3>Operational Adjustments</h3>

      <p>Off-peak operations require:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Night Dispatch:</strong> Dispatcher available 10pm-6am</li>
        <li><strong>Driver Availability:</strong> Drivers willing to work night shifts</li>
        <li><strong>Client Coordination:</strong> Wareports must accept late-night/early-morning deliveries</li>
        <li><strong>Port Access:</strong> Ports must allow off-peak container pickup/drop-off</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Additional Prime Movers for Peak/Off-Peak Split</h3>

      <p>Optimal strategy: Split fleet between peak and off-peak operations:</p>

      <p><strong>Example Fleet (10 Prime Movers):</strong>
      <br>• 6 prime movers: Peak hours (6am-10am, 4pm-8pm)
      <br>• 4 prime movers: Off-peak hours (10pm-6am)
      <br><strong>Incentive Earnings:</strong> 4 prime movers × 2 trips/day × RM15 × 25 days = RM3,000/month</p>

      <h2>Ing Heng Credit: Off-Peak Optimization Financing</h2>

      <h3>1. We Finance Complete Off-Peak Setup</h3>

      <p>We finance:
      <br>• Prime mover purchase
      <br>• OBU installation
      <br>• JPJ registration modifications
      <br>• Initial off-peak permit fees</p>

      <p><strong>Result:</strong> One monthly payment covers all off-peak requirements.</p>

      <h3>2. 0% Down Payment Accelerates Off-Peak Transition</h3>

      <p>Transitioning to off-peak operations requires:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>OBU equipment purchase: RM3,500 per prime mover
        <li>Driver night shift differential pay: +RM500/month per driver
        <li>Dispatcher night shift: Additional staff cost</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>0% Down Payment Benefit:</strong>
      <br>• Preserved capital covers transition costs
      <br>• Off-peak incentives (RM18,750/month) exceed transition costs within 2 months
      <br>• Profitability begins immediately</p>

      <h3>3. Flexible Terms for Seasonal Adjustments</h3>

      <p>Off-peak demand varies by season:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Festive periods: High demand (off-peak valuable)
        <li>Monsoon seasons: Reduced demand (may revert to peak operations)
        <li>Economic slowdowns: Port volumes drop (off-peak may be only option)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>We offer:
      <br>• Seasonal payment adjustments
      <br>• Skip payments during low-volume months
      <br>• Balloon payments during high-volume months</p>

      <h3>4. Multiple Prime Mover Financing</h3>

      <p>Optimal off-peak/peak split requires multiple prime movers:</p>

      <p><strong>Example: 10 Prime Mover Fleet</strong>
      <br>• 4 off-peak dedicated: RM1.4 million
      <br>• 6 peak/off-peak flexible: RM2.1 million
      <br><strong>Total Investment:</strong> RM3.5 million</p>

      <p>We finance entire fleet with 0% down payment, bundle all OBU equipment, and structure payments to match off-peak revenue patterns.</p>

      <h2>Real-World Off-Peak Success Stories</h2>

