      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Want to Maximize Off-Peak Incentives?</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">We finance prime movers with OBU equipment and 0% down payment. Start earning RM15/trip off-peak incentives immediately.</p>
